</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%;background-color:#F5DEB3;">Commentary</th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-odd" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Sarv%C4%81rthasiddhi" title="Sarvārthasiddhi">Sarvārthasiddhi</a> (commentary on Tattvārthasūtra)</li></ul>
</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%;background-color:#F5DEB3;">Others</th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-even" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
